OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright and chilly start with
OL,6,Fa touch of frost possible. Sunny
OL,7,Fspells will turn hazy during the day
OL,8,Fwith patchy light rain pushing into
OL,9,FSkye, Lochaber and the Uist's during
OL,10,Fthe afternoon. Feeling pleasant in any
OL,11,Fsunshine, light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FOutbreaks of rain pushing
OL,14,Fnortheast this evening, the odd
OL,15,Fheavier burst in the west. Remaining
OL,16,Fcloudy overnight with outbreaks of
OL,17,Frain and much milder than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
