OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA cloudy start with outbreaks
OL,6,Fof rain. It will turn more showery
OL,7,Fduring the day with some brighter
OL,8,Fspells. The showers could be heavy,
OL,9,Fperhaps the odd rumble of thunder.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMainly
OL,12,Fdry and bright on Monday with early
OL,13,Fshowers dying out. Rain or showers on
OL,14,FTuesday and Wednesday, heavy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
